        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued July 28 at 3:24PM EDT until July 28 at 3:45PM EDT by NWS Detroit/Pontiac MI</headline>
        <description>At 324 PM EDT, severe thunderstorms were located along a line
extending from near Brighton to near Salem to near Canton, moving
east at 15 mph.

HAZARD...60 mph wind gusts.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Expect damage to roofs, siding, and trees.

These severe storms will be near...
South Lyon and Salem around 330 PM EDT.

Other locations impacted by these severe thunderstorms include Barton
Hills, Island Lake State Recreation Area, and Delhi Mills.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
